'''Wakamiya Inari Shrine''' (若宮稲荷神社) is the name of several {{ill|Shinto shrines|ja|神社}}.
* {{ill|Wakamiya Inari Shrine (Kazamaura)|ja|若宮稲荷神社 (風間浦村)}} - Located in Kazamaura, Shimokita District, Aomori Prefecture, at Shimonofuro, Yunoue. * {{ill|Wakamiya Inari Shrine (Nakadomari)|ja|若宮稲荷神社 (中泊町)}} - Located in Nakadomari, Kitatsugaru District, Aomori Prefecture, at Tamogi, Wakamiya. * {{ill|Wakamiya Inari Shrine (Izumo)|ja|若宮稲荷神社 (出雲市)}} - Located in Izumo City, Shimane Prefecture, in Takamatsu Town. * {{ill|Wakamiya Inari Shrine (Nagasaki)|ja|若宮稲荷神社 (長崎市)}} - Located in Nagasaki City, Nagasaki Prefecture, in Irabayashi. Also known as Irabayashi Inari Shrine, it is renowned for the [[:en:Takengei|Takengei]] performance. * {{ill|Wakamiya Inari Shrine|ja|若宮稲荷神社 (ハワイ)|en}} - Located in Waipahu, Hawaii, United States.
